    {
      "id": "01046370-825c-4fd6-ad26-ae0c09712613",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Nowadays, there is more and more data available from VLE. This data has been used already to create early warning systems that intend to identify students at risk. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "01046370-825c-4fd6-ad26-ae0c09712613",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
